title: 74/129. Enlargement of the Executive Committee of the Programme of the United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees

paragraphs.1: Decides to increase the number of members of the Executive Committee of the Programme of the United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees from 102 States to 106 States;
paragraphs.2: Requests the Economic and Social Council to elect the additional members at a meeting of its management segment in 2020.
